		{"id":"10dcba87a630e47d","type":"text","text":"## 🌐 Core Custom Website Features\n\n\t Fully custom UI (brand colors, logo, layout)\n\t Responsive design (mobile + tablet + desktop)\n\t Fast loading (optimized performance)\n\t SEO-friendly structure\n\t Advanced / Premium Features","x":-600,"y":4180,"width":480,"height":229},
