		{"id":"671186cdd5326c27","type":"text","text":" # Growth\n **We actually help you to grow. **","x":1367,"y":3655,"width":280,"height":110},
		{"id":"68ce7557d78b2f2c","type":"text","text":"petpooja can never grow your sales they can only make you feel smooth but never actually make your business grow\n\n\nWe use [[Marketing]] with your customer number","x":1322,"y":4172,"width":358,"height":237},
		{"id":"aa06b520e10cdf64","type":"text","text":"With Petpooja the restro can never make the repeatable customer growth\n\nWe craft intuitive, refined experiences that elevate dining, create exclusivity, and inspire customers to return again and again. ","x":900,"y":4172,"width":380,"height":237},
		{"id":"e54fceb42531cdbd","type":"text","text":"so actually help you\n\t\t`Increase repeat customers` \n\t\t`Higher average order value` \n\t\t`Faster service` \n\t\t`Better reviews` ","x":1720,"y":4172,"width":360,"height":237},
		{"id":"5d056e43d1491315","type":"text","text":"**We give your restro customer a Modern Experience**","x":2960,"y":3697,"width":280,"height":63},
		{"id":"8a0436cb03b8a0ea","type":"text","text":"## Efficiency & Accuracy\n\n- **Zero-Error Ordering:** Because the customer selects their own items, there is no risk of a server mishearing an order or forgetting a specific modification.\n    \n- **Real-Time Availability:** If a dish is sold out, it can be hidden from the digital menu instantly, preventing the disappointment of ordering something that isn't available.\n    \n- **Faster Service:** Orders go straight to the kitchen (KOT), meaning the cooking process starts minutes sooner than with traditional pen-and-paper systems.","x":2240,"y":4134,"width":505,"height":314},
		{"id":"1cfb5d244206fce2","type":"text","text":"## Digital Empowerment\n\n- **Instant Menu Access:** Customers scan a QR code to view a high-quality digital menu immediately—no waiting for a physical menu or a busy server.\n    \n- **Self-Paced Ordering:** Guests can browse descriptions and photos at their own speed, reducing the \"ordering anxiety\" that often happens during a rush.\n    \n- **Visual Appeal:** Beautifully rendered food photos in the digital interface make the menu more appetizing and easier to navigate than a text-heavy paper menu.","x":2848,"y":4134,"width":505,"height":314},
		{"id":"88a8d25db2c84fca","type":"text","text":"## Personalization & Vibe\n\n- **Customization Made Easy:** Clearly labeled \"Add-ons\" or \"Special Instructions\" sections allow customers to tailor their meal exactly how they like it.\n    \n- **Less Intrusion:** Servers can focus on delivering food and hospitality rather than administrative tasks like taking orders or processing payments, making the atmosphere feel more relaxed.","x":3440,"y":4134,"width":400,"height":314},
		{"id":"b71c158fef7c42f2","type":"text","text":"# - Staff Management \n    Employee Information \n    Attendance Management\n    Payroll & Salary\n    Leave Management\n    Performance Tracking\n","x":-960,"y":4180,"width":331,"height":229}
	],
